item.title: I-8 East - Exit 115
item.description: I-8 east at Exit 115 - AZ-85/Ajo/Phoenix. I-8 continues east towards Tucson. This is the western end of the Gila Bend business loop.

item.title: I-10 West Approaching Exit 112
item.description: I-10 west approaching Exit 112 - Use Exit 112 for AZ-85/To I-8/Gila Bend/Mexico. The border crossing served by this exit is Lukeville,AZ/Sonoyta,Sonora.
